cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a novel pose estimation method for geometric vision of omni-directional cameras. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the estimation of camera motion, which is relevant to robotics applications. 
3. cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with panoramic images and their 3D transformation. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and motion estimation. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new algorithm for pose estimation, which can be considered as an AI technique.
